{
  "meta": {
    "ep": 1,
    "title": "A Quiet Afternoon",
    "kind": "main"
  },
  "messages": [
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "The semester is finally over.",
      "marks": [
        {
          "word": "semester",
          "index": 1,
          "definition": "学期",
          "is_new": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I bike to a family restaurant in the next town.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Self-service drinks. Extra-large fries.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "This — right here — is real leisure.",
      "marks": [
        {
          "word": "leisure",
          "index": 7,
          "definition": "闲暇",
          "is_new": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Not the loud type the popular kids need an audience for. Just a story and me.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Every page I can anticipate. Every sentence I can appreciate.",
      "marks": [
        {
          "word": "anticipate",
          "index": 4,
          "definition": "期待",
          "is_new": true
        },
        {
          "word": "appreciate",
          "index": 9,
          "definition": "欣赏",
          "is_new": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Nobody asking why I'm smiling.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Cola. Fries. Light novel. The unholy trinity.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "My mood lifts just looking at the cover.",
      "marks": [
        {
          "word": "mood",
          "index": 1,
          "definition": "心情",
          "is_new": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I bite a fry. Open the book.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "The heroine tells her useless brother he deserves love. Pure wish-fulfillment.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "But that's the point.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "The real world doesn't offer unconditional acceptance.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "The real world offers exams. Social hierarchies. Not knowing where to stand in the cafeteria.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "So I focus.",
      "marks": [
        {
          "word": "focus",
          "index": 2,
          "definition": "集中",
          "is_new": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Each page I turn is a step further from reality.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I consume fries. Methodically. One by one.",
      "marks": [
        {
          "word": "consume",
          "index": 1,
          "definition": "消耗, 吃",
          "is_new": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Kurumi delivers a line that would make any lonely brother weep.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Junk food plus emotional manipulation. A winning formula.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Everything is perfect.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "side": "left",
      "name": "Anna",
      "text": "GO AFTER HER OR SHE'S LEAVING FOR ENGLAND!",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "My fry freezes mid-air.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I know that voice.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Anna Yanami. One of the cutest girls in our grade.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Sits in the center of our classroom. Lives in a world I never enter.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "Right behind my booth.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "I lower my fry.",
      "marks": []
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "text": "My quiet afternoon. Over.",
      "marks": []
    }
  ],
